         <p>Arranged aphabetically by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_fc1e0a481ab87ea0d1e7d0426e38f59f">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Correspondence, speeches, photographs, awards, clippings, and miscellanea documenting the professional career of Thomas Walter Swan, a lawyer, judge, and dean of the Yale Law School, 1916-1927.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
